      "type": "text",
      "data": "<ol class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\"><li><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: tahoma, 宋体; font-size: 13px; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(239, 239, 239);\"><a href=\"http://www.apuebook.com/\">http://www.apuebook.com/</a>&nbsp;下载apue.3e并解压</span></p></li><li><p>sudo apt-get install libbsd-dev(如果不安装此软件，make会报错)</p><p>make</p></li></ol><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\">3.将 cp &nbsp;apue.3e/include/apue.h &nbsp;/usr/include&nbsp;<br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;cp &nbsp;apue.3e/lib/error.c &nbsp; &nbsp; /usr/include</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\">配置完毕</p>"
    }
